Description: Methods to infer clonal structure for a population of cells
    using single-cell RNA-seq data (and possibly other data modalities).
    Methods to assign cells to inferred clones and explore differences in
    gene expression between clones.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/single-cell-genetics/cardelino
